transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, Joanna speaking, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hi, I would like to cancel my subscription, please.

Speaker 1: Okay, I can assist you with that, sir. Let me pull up your account. Can you please verify your name and date of birth?

Speaker 2: My date of birth is 01-03-1973.

Speaker 1: Okay, one moment.
